'''Ladji Diakité''' , ni umukinnyi wa firime wo muri [[Mali]] . Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime zamamaye cyane nka ''Duel à Dafa'' na ''Fantan Fanga'' <ref>https://africanfilmny.org/directors/ladji-diakite/</ref>.  Usibye gutanga icyerekezo, Diakité ni umuyobozi wungirije hamwe nuwashushanyaga imyambarire<ref>http://africultures.com/personnes?no=17752</ref>. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye i [[Bamako]], muri Mali. Diakité yabonye impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu buvanganzo yakuye muri Ecole Normale Supérieure<ref>https://www.festival-cannes.com/en/artist/ladji-diakite</ref> . Yize kandi muri Centre national du cinéma et de l'image animée (Ikigo cyigihugu gishinzwe gutunganya film)<ref>https://iffr.com/en/persons/ladji-diakit%C3%A9</ref>. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1991, yinjiye muri filime ''Ta Dona nk'ushushanya'' imyambarire.  Hanyuma mu 1997, yakoze muri film ''Taafé Fanga'' nk'umuyobozi wungirije<ref>https://ifcinema.institutfrancais.com/fr/search?q_text=Ladji%20Diakite</ref>.

Mu 2001, yayoboye filime ''yumukobwa La Rencontre des chasseurs''<ref>http://www.clapnoir.org/spip.php?mot144</ref> . Mu 2006, yagiye muri firime ya tele ''Duel a Dafa'' .  Hanyuma mu 2007, yayoboye ''Duel à Dafa'' hanyuma ''Fantan Fanga'' afatanya na Adama Drabo mu 2009<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0224467/</ref>.  Iyi filime yakiriwe ku mugaragaro iserukiramuco rya Filime na Televiziyo bya Panafrican rya Ouagadougou (FESPACO) 2009. Hagati aho, yabaye umuyobozi w’ishami rishinzwe umusaruro w’ikigo Centre de la cinématographie du Mali (Ikigo cy’igihugu cya Cinematografi ya [[Mali]]: CNCM)<ref>http://www.africine.org/personne/ladji-diakite/17752</ref>. 

